### Listar itens (Sem filtros)
GET http://localhost:3333/items
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJkOGI4ZDY3Zi1iNWU5LTQwNzUtYWE5OC1kNjgwYWRkMzM3MzYiLCJyb2xlIjoiRG9hZG9yIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc0NDg4ODYwfQ.HikJnsPuAo5JStSQH4fY9iNcKP1MD4McV-7FQqXbJI0
### Listar itens apenas da categoria "Móveis"
GET http://localhost:3333/items?category=Móveis
Authorization: Bearer EU_TOKEN_AQUI
### Listar itens perto de mim (Sorocaba)
GET http://localhost:3333/items?lat=-23.501533&lng=-47.458112
Authorization: Bearer EU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Ver detalhes de um item específico
GET http://localhost:3333/items/40d5de3f-0408-4dd0-a2e5-dd1fabf0bcf3
