### Alterar Status de um Item (Disponível -> Reservado)
PATCH http://localhost:3333/items/40d5de3f-0408-4dd0-a2e5-dd1fabf0bcf3/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJkZWRkMGNlYy02MmMyLTRlNDgtOGU2OC1hOTFlN2E0MjM0OTkiLCJyb2xlIjoiRG9hZG9yIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc0NDg5NTE0fQ.AcqxBWWadXSHg4_c5Fbq4U2NWN-YJFHQEzg5y5qA4Y8

{
  "status": "Reservado"
}

